query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS leads (
  id int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  leadType enum('buyer', 'seller', 'mortgage') NOT NULL,
  firstName varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  lastName varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  email varchar(320) NOT NULL,
  phone varchar(20),
  city varchar(100),
  state varchar(2),
  zipCode varchar(10),
  interestedPropertyId int,
  budgetMin decimal(12, 2),
  budgetMax decimal(12, 2),
  timelineMonths int,
  propertyAddress varchar(255),
  propertyCity varchar(100),
  estimatedValue decimal(12, 2),
  homePrice decimal(12, 2),
  downPayment decimal(12, 2),
  interestRate decimal(5, 2),
  loanTerm int,
  monthlyPayment decimal(10, 2),
  qualityScore enum('hot', 'warm', 'cold') DEFAULT 'warm' NOT NULL,
  qualityReason text,
  status enum('new', 'contacted', 'qualified', 'converted', 'lost') DEFAULT 'new' NOT NULL,
  source varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  sourcePropertyId int,
  isPurchased boolean DEFAULT false NOT NULL,
  purchasedBy int,
  purchasedAt timestamp,
  purchasePrice decimal(10, 2),
  ghlContactId varchar(255),
  ghlPipelineId varchar(255),
  capturedAt timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  createdAt timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  CONSTRAINT leads_id PRIMARY KEY(id),
  KEY leads_leadType_idx (leadType),
  KEY leads_status_idx (status),
  KEY leads_qualityScore_idx (qualityScore),
  KEY leads_email_idx (email),
  KEY leads_isPurchased_idx (isPurchased),
  KEY leads_purchasedBy_idx (purchasedBy)
);
